  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAggregationStrategy
    Strategy for aggregating new GPSSegments to an AggContainer.
    IMergeHandler
    Class for handling the merge of a set of GPSPoints from the trace being added and a correspondig set of AggNode objects from an AggContainer.
    ITraceDistance  
  • Class Summary

    AggCleaner
    Class for cleaning a path in the AggContainer using give CleaningOptions.
    AggConnection
    A connection between two AggNodes.
    AggContainer
    Container class for an aggregation graph.

    Models a pair of a Point and its GhostPoint.

    Shallow version of an AggNode.
    TraceDistanceFactory
